---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Carpet Cleaning Laval | Professional Truck-Mount Service"
  description="Carpet and rug cleaning in Laval. Fast residential service with our truck-mounts to easily eliminate stains, allergens, and sand. Free evaluation."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO -->
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT (Hook) -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">CARPET & STAIRS • LAVAL</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Residential Carpet Cleaning in Laval
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100">
            <h3 class="problem-title">Daily Wear and Tear:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              Harsh winters and pets leave their mark: sand, calcium, and oils accumulate at the base of your carpets and prematurely wear out the fibers in your stairs and living rooms.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            Groupe Nettoyage Empire deploys its ultra-high-performance truck-mounts throughout Laval to bring your carpeted floors back to life. Our powerful steam extraction system leaves your carpets clean, soft, and free of chemical residues.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Laval Quote)
            </a>
            <button
              onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()"
              class="btn btn-gradient-green"
            >
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Fast Online Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Visual / Slideshow) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-vapeur-laval.webp"
              alt="Steam carpet cleaning with professional equipment in Laval"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-143.webp"
              alt="Clean and healthy carpet result in Laval"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-34.webp"
              alt="Empire Cleaning technician at work"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="service-main">
          <!-- BENEFIT LIST & SEO CONTENT -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
             <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              The Power of the Truck-Mount for Your Home
            </h2>

            <p>
              For homes in Laval, the <strong>truck-mount method</strong> is the absolute gold standard. This self-contained system provides boiling heat (steam) and suction that is vastly superior to portable machines, ensuring deep cleaning and ultra-fast drying.
            </p>

            <ul class="benefit-list" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
               <li>
                <strong>1. Targeted Pre-treatment:</strong> Application of enzymes on highly trafficked areas to loosen oily residues.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>2. Gentle Agitation:</strong> To lift crushed fibers on stairs or in the basement.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>3. Steam Extraction:</strong> Very hot water pulsed and vacuumed back into the truck, eliminating 99% of dust mites and embedded dirt.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>4. Rinse:</strong> Your carpets regain their original softness (never stiff).
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>5. Drying:</strong> The strong suction of the truck ensures a typical drying time of 3-6 hours.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
              <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                ⭐ The Challenge of Carpeted Stairs
              </h3>
              <p>
                In multi-story homes in Laval, the nose of the steps is the first area to darken and flatten. 
              </p>
              <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                Our technicians use a hand tool specially molded for steps, treating the nose, the riser, and all corners with precision to restore the appearance of your entire staircase.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEW SECTIONS: BENEFITS & FAQ -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout" style="display: block;">
        <div class="service-main" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
          
          <!-- ZONES DESSERVIES -->
          <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">We Serve All of Laval and the North Shore</h3>
            <p>Our mobile teams quickly cover all neighborhoods in Laval and surrounding areas:</p>

            <div class="city-group">
              <div class="badges-container">
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Chomedey</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sainte-Rose</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Vimont & Auteuil</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Fabreville</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sainte-Dorothée</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Duvernay & Saint-Vincent-de-Paul</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Laval-West</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Rosemère, Blainville, Boisbriand (North Shore)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="contact-footer">Free estimate for Laval: <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-300" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Frequently Asked Questions — Laval
            </h2>
            <FAQSchema
              faqs={[
                 {
                  question:
                    "How does truck-mount cleaning work in front of my house in Laval?",
                  answer:
                    "We park our truck in your driveway. Our heavy equipment, the pump motor, and the dirty water tank remain in the truck. We only bring our clean hoses and handheld applicators into your home, reducing noise and ensuring maximum suction.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "Can you eliminate dog/cat odor embedded in a basement carpet?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes, we use deep-injected enzymatic treatments (not just surface perfumes) that biologically break down the bacteria causing urine odors or pet dander odors marinating in the underpad.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "Do you apply a protector (Teflon/Scotchgard) after cleaning?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes, we offer the application of a high-quality protector as an option. This is particularly advisable for main pathways (hallways, stairs) as it delays wear and gives you time to wipe up a liquid spill before it stains.",
                }
              ]}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  if (slides.length > 0) {
    let currentSlide = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, 4000);
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* Base styles reused */
  .split-hero-container { background-color: #fff; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; overflow: hidden; width: 100vw; }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; min-height: 80vh; }
  .split-content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .service-cat-badge { text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .split-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .problem-statement { background: #ffffff; border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .cta-group { display: none !important; } }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slide { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out; }
  .slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .split-content { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; order: 1; }
    .split-image-wrapper { order: 2; height: 400px; min-height: 0; }
    .lead-text { max-width: 100%; }
  }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .separator { border: 0; height: 1px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .benefit-list { margin: 2rem 0; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .benefit-list li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .benefit-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: #d32f2f; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: bold; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }
</style>
